## Resource Key Taxonomy

Every subscribable resource has a canonical key format: `<resource_type>:<id>`.

| Resource type        | Example key            | Domain                             |
| -------------------- | ---------------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| `forum_category`     | `forum_category:5`     | Forum — category list + threads    |
| `thread`             | `thread:42`            | Forum — single thread + comments   |
| `user`               | `user:17`              | User profile (viewed by others)    |
| `inbox_conversation` | `inbox_conversation:3` | Inbox — messages in a conversation |
| `store_product`      | `store_product:8`      | Store — single product detail      |
| `store_category`     | `store_category:2`     | Store — per-category updates       |
| `page`               | `page:slug`            | CMS — custom page content          |

Resources that use broadcast (no subscription required):

| Scope           | Events included                                                         |
| --------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Store catalog   | `product_created`, `product_updated`, `product_deleted`                 |
|                 | `category_created`, `category_updated`, `category_deleted`              |
| Site config     | `branding_updated`, `seo_updated`, `footer_updated`, `features_updated` |
| CMS pages       | `page_created`, `page_updated`, `page_deleted`                          |
| Forum broadcast | `thread_created`, `thread_deleted` (live feed fallback path)            |

Resources that use direct push (server → user, no subscription):

| Message type                        | Trigger                                |
| ----------------------------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| `notification`                      | Any notification event for this user   |
| `inbox:message`                     | New DM received (badge + sidebar ping) |
| `store:update` (cart actions)       | `cart_updated` after any cart mutation |
| `user:update` (permissions_changed) | JWT + role/permission refresh          |

