## Full Message Type Registry

All messages are JSON frames:
`{ type: string, payload: string (JSON-encoded) }`

### Client → Server

| `type`          | Payload fields                 | Purpose                       |
| --------------- | ------------------------------ | ----------------------------- |
| `subscribe`     | `resource_type`, `resource_id` | Subscribe to resource key     |
| `unsubscribe`   | `resource_type`, `resource_id` | Unsubscribe from resource key |
| `ping`          | —                              | Heartbeat keepalive (30 s)    |
| `presence`      | `route`, `user_name`, `avatar` | Announce current route        |
| `global:chat`   | `content`                      | Send global chat message      |
| `cursor:update` | `x` (float64), `y` (float64)   | Broadcast cursor position     |
| `tp`            | `target_user_id`, `route`      | Admin teleport command        |

### Server → Client

| `type`                | Payload                                           | Delivery mode         |
| --------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- | --------------------- |
| `forum:update`        | `{ action, id, data }` — see Forum Actions        | subscription          |
| `store:update`        | `{ action, data }` — see Store Actions            | broadcast / direct    |
| `user:update`         | `{ action, data }` — see User Actions             | subscription / direct |
| `config:update`       | `{ action, data }` — see Config Actions           | broadcast             |
| `page:update`         | `{ action, data }` — see Page Actions             | broadcast             |
| `inbox:update`        | `{ action, data: InboxMessage }`                  | subscription          |
| `inbox:message`       | `{ conversation_id, ... }` (InboxMessage summary) | direct push           |
| `notification`        | full `AppNotification` object                     | direct push           |
| `presence:update`     | `{ users: PresenceUser[] }`                       | broadcast             |
| `cursor:update`       | `{ user_id, user_name, avatar, x, y }`            | same-route relay      |
| `global:chat`         | single `GlobalChatMessage`                        | broadcast             |
| `global:chat:history` | `{ messages: GlobalChatMessage[] }`               | direct (on connect)   |
| `tp`                  | `{ route }`                                       | direct push           |

